Alchemist	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Artificer Class Feature.Class Feature.Artificer Subclass.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:An Alchemist is an expert at combining reagents to produce magical effects. Alchemists use their creations to give life and to leech it away.	KEY:Artificer Subclass ~ Alchemist																		ABILITY:Artificer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Alchemist ~ Tool Proficiency|PREVAREQ:ArtificerLVL,3	ABILITY:Artificer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Alchemist ~ Alchemist Spells|PREVAREQ:ArtificerLVL,3	ABILITY:Artificer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Alchemist ~ Experimental elixir|PREVAREQ:ArtificerLVL,3	ABILITY:Artificer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Alchemist ~ Alchemical Savant|PREVAREQ:ArtificerLVL,5	ABILITY:Artificer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Alchemist ~ Restorative Reagent|PREVAREQ:ArtificerLVL,9	ABILITY:Artificer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Alchemist ~ Chemical Mastery|PREVAREQ:ArtificerLVL,15			SORTKEY:Class_Artificer_01d1	SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Armorer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Artificer Class Feature.Class Feature.Artificer Subclass.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:An Artificer who specializes as an Armorer modifies armor to function almost like a second skin. The armor is enhanced to hone the Artificer’s magic, unleash potent attacks, and generate a formidable defense.	KEY:Artificer Subclass ~ Armorer																		ABILITY:Artificer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Armorer ~ Tools of the Trade|PREVAREQ:ArtificerLVL,3	ABILITY:Artificer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Armorer ~ Armorer Spells|PREVAREQ:ArtificerLVL,3	ABILITY:Artificer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Armorer ~ Arcane Armor|PREVAREQ:ArtificerLVL,3	ABILITY:Artificer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Armorer ~ Armor Model|PREVAREQ:ArtificerLVL,3	ABILITY:Artificer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Armorer ~ Extra Attack|PREVAREQ:ArtificerLVL,5	ABILITY:Artificer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Armorer ~ Armor Replication|PREVAREQ:ArtificerLVL,9	ABILITY:Artificer Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Armorer ~ Perfected Armor|PREVAREQ:ArtificerLVL,15		SORTKEY:Class_Artificer_01d2	SOURCEPAGE:PHB
